<node CREATED="1576216631060" ID="ID_349974588" MODIFIED="1576216631060" TEXT="Simply put cloud computing is computing based on the internet.Where in the past people would run applications or programs from software downloaded on a physical computer or server in their building cloud computing allows people access to the same kinds of applications through the internet." />
