<node CREATED="1576216631060" ID="ID_1835890880" MODIFIED="1576216631060" TEXT="The primary reason why cloud computing is getting so much attention is its effect on business strategies. The sheer cost pressure alone is forcing industry after industry to adapt to the new reality. The advantages notwithstanding several valid concerns about cloud computing exist namely having to do with privacy and security." />
