<node CREATED="1576216631060" ID="ID_1045321421" MODIFIED="1576216631060" TEXT="Cloud computing benefits Flexibility. Users can scale services to fit their needs customize applications and access cloud services from anywhere with an internet connection. Efficiency. Enterprise users can get applications to market quickly without worrying about underlying infrastructure costs or maintenance." />
</node>
