<node CREATED="1576216631060" ID="ID_1241370213" MODIFIED="1576216631060" TEXT="Cloud computing is the on-demand availability of computer system resources especially data storage and computing power without direct active management by the user. The term is generally used to describe data centers available to many users over the Internet. Large clouds predominant today often have functions distributed over multiple " />
</node>
